id: 2607
name: Proposal Chambers
power: 2.0
text: |
  Chamber is a a secured untracked ordinary proposal switch whose
  possible values include unset (the default) and each of the
  ministries of Agora.

  A proposal's chamber SHOULD only be decided by which ministry's
  goals it effects to the greatest degree.

  If a proposal in the Proposal Pool has its chamber unset, the
  Promotor CAN set the chamber to a specified ministry by
  announcement. Any player CAN, with 2 Agoran consent, flip the
  chamber of an ordinary proposal to any ministry, provided that
  it is in the Proposal Pool or that there is an Agoran decision
  on its adoption whose voting period has not yet ended.
